title: Graphing Basics with the TI-84 CE graphing calculator
description: You’re probably going to have to graph a function and locate points on it for your big test. This fun video shows you step by step how to set up your TI-84 Plus CE graphing calculator to use the TRACE feature for saving time and avoiding mistakes.
